{
  "stem": "8805.1",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then we drove to a different town where they have the train.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they would bombarding all the time.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So some people didn't want to drive.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So they went from the trucks.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they said, they going to go home.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But it happens I was staying on the truck.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then while we were driving, I met two more of my friends.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we decided whatever happened, we're going to be together.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then we came to a city-- [NON-ENGLISH]-- no.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I forgot the name-- where there was the train.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And the Russian said we should-- who wants to be evacuated should go on the train.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we went on the train.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Until people packed on, on the train, they start to bombard again.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So then-- then it was-- it was terrible, because some got killed.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Some, you know, and some from the train-- the-- what do you call it?",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The-- They disconnected, and they connected the-- the part from the train.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "How do you call them?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "The cars?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The cars.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And-- it was-- and they said, they going to evacuated us.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So we were driving-- I don't know-- for a day, for two days, till we--",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Some of them took, because they bombard some of the cars.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So then when-- when they came in the morning, we were near Kiev, in Russia.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "In the meantime, a lot of people went back.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They didn't want to go.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And it just happened I was-- we-- three of us were together.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we stick together.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And then Stalin give-- said, we should-- everybody, the train's going to be free.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "You should go wherever you want in Russia.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And they used to give food on the stations.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They were very helpful.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So we took a train to Kharkov.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
